Contains the collection of models myself, Chris*, and Moonjammy originally posted to Thingiverse that have been taken down by Grandma Wendy. I've uploaded them here to give a single spot to download for folks again.

Provides spotters and drivers in
-Segmented Armour
-Boarding Armour
-Plate Armour
-Ballbearing Armour
-Beaky Armour

Gun platforms containing heavy machine guns, gravity cannons, laser cannon, and mortars.

Contains parts from Dangitblobby, jimmyzims, Chris*, Moonjammy

If you like what I did and want to leave a tip it would be appreciated.
https://paypal.me/jimmyzimms

* Name redacted to protect the party from Grandma Wendy

Print ready for resin printers. Just import, make sure the base is on the print bed, slice then print. 2xAA and 0.02mm layer height reccommended.
These files are not intended for FDM slicers or printers.

Please bear in mind that these miniatures have extremely fragile parts despite my best efforts to make everything as solid as possible. Handle with care.
